snippet.title: Airheart - Tales of broken Wings - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-purchase it now on the Nintendo eShop:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/nintendo-switch-new-releases

Airheart is a dieselpunk airplane action game, where every colorful level is built on top of the previous one, all the way up to the stratosphere.

An airplane game, reimagined in a wonderful world, Airheart is a treat to fans and newcomers to flight action games alike.

Also available on Steam, XBox and PlayStation:
- Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/531180/AIRHEART__Tales_of_broken_Wings/
- Xbox One: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/airheart-tales-of-broken-wings/bw8g2qjkj21s
- PlayStation 4: https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/airheart-tales-of-broken-wings-ps4/
